<list id="fs-idm268538480" list-type="bulleted">
<item>Document 1: The Declaration of Independence (1776)</item>
<item>Document 2: Thomas Jefferson‚Äôs Query XVIII from <emphasis effect="italics">Notes on the State of Virginia</emphasis> (1781)</item>
<item>Document 3: Thomas Jefferson‚Äôs letter to Bishop Henri Gr√©goire (1809)</item>
<item>Document 4: David Walker‚Äôs <emphasis effect="italics">An Appeal to the Coloured Citizens of the World</emphasis> (1829)</item>
<item>Document 5: Sarah Moore Grimk√©‚Äôs ‚ÄúAn Epistle to the Clergy of the Southern States‚Äù (1836)</item>
